== Hotspotd 0.2.0 ==

1. Rewritten to use Click library
2. All code moved to hotspotd.py file
3. Interfaces automatic selection algorithm changed
4. New configuration file location /etc/hotspotd.json
5. setup.py rewritten from scratch to use setuptools instead of distutis


